node.text:
Roar with us if you love tigers on #GlobalTigerDay 🐅
 
The wild Malayan tiger population in Malaysia has dropped by 50% in 10 years, which is why we’re working with @wwfmy to protect this critically important and endangered species. Together, we’re preserving tiger habitats in Peninsular Malaysia and supporting local anti-poaching efforts to help ensure the Malayan tigers’ survival for years to come. Our work is part of a program that has helped reduce poaching by 60%. Learn more at the link in our bio #ItsOurHome
